						<summary>

						<p>On the door-jamb of the <hi rend="italic">prasāda</hi> room in the second <hi rend="italic">prākāra</hi> of the Saptarishīśvara temple.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Year 16: 987 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>Damaged at the bottom. Appears to refer to a gift by Neḍuñjērikkuḍāṉ kōṉ Chōḻappaṉichchiyānambiyaṉ to the temple of Nagara-Tirumaḻuvaṉūr-Bhaṭṭāraka of Nagaravāḻkkai in the Mi-kūṟṟu in Kalār-kūṟṟam, (a sub-division) of Vaḍagarai-Maḻanāḍu.</p>						

						</summary>
